{"word":"G1455 - ἐγκάθετος - enkáthetos - eng-kath'-et-os - Spy","sections":[{"paragraph":"<strong>மூல வார்த்தை / Original: </strong><span class=\"hebrewOrGreek\">ἐγκάθετος</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>எழுத்துமாற்றம் / Transliteration: </strong><span class=\"transliteration\">enkáthetos</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>ஒலிபெயர்ப்பு / Phonetic: </strong><span class=\"phonetic\">eng-kath'-et-os</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>சுருக்க விளக்கம் / Short Definition: </strong><span class=\"short-definition\">Spy</span>"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"parts-of-speech\"><strong>இலக்கண சொல்வகை / Part(s) of speech: </strong>Adjective / பெயரடை</span>"},{"paragraph":"பதிவிருத்தல், வேவுபார்த்தல்"},{"paragraph":"suborned to lie in wait; a lier - in - wait, a spy"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"original-in-english\"><strong>ஆங்கில மூலம் / Original in English: </strong>From <a href=\"#/G1722 - ἐν - en - en/1722\">G1722</a> and a derivative of <a href=\"#/G2524 - καθίημι - kathíēmi - kath-ee'-ay-mee/2524\">G2524</a>; <i>subinduced</i>, that is, surreptitiously <i>suborned</i> as a lier in wait: - spy.</span>"},{"paragraph":""}]}